## Problem Statement Selected

### HR Cost Intelligence / Meeting-to-Project Cost Attribution

Organizations lack visibility into how meeting time translates into real HR spend per project. Timesheets are manual and unreliable, while calendar data already captures where employees spend their time. This problem requires connecting:

**Calendar Meetings → AI-Powered Project Attribution → Employee Cost Mapping → Executive Insights**

to help leadership understand the true cost of collaboration.

---

## Project Description

### FinOps AI

FinOps AI is an AI-powered HR Cost Intelligence platform that helps organizations answer one critical business question:

> **"What are our meetings actually costing us, and which projects are driving that spend?"**

The platform automatically synchronizes Google Calendar meetings, uses AI to attribute meetings to projects, calculates employee costs based on hourly rates, and provides executive dashboards, anomaly detection, forecasting, and AI-powered insights.

Instead of relying on inaccurate manual timesheets, organizations can use existing calendar data as the source of truth for understanding project-level HR spending.

The system provides:

* Automated meeting-to-project attribution
* HR cost allocation by project
* Executive cost dashboards
* Cost anomaly detection
* Forecasting and recommendations
* Natural language AI Copilot
* Voice-enabled FinOps Assistant
* Human review workflow for low-confidence AI decisions
* Role-based access control and audit trails

